deck: An actor who has played roles such as Judge Dredd and Leonard McCoy.
description:
Comic Related Movie Roles

Judge Dredd

Urban played Judge Dredd in the film Dredd.

Leonard McCoy

In Star Trek and Star Trek Into Darkness (the films in the rebooted Star Trek universe) Urban played Leonard McCoy.
name: Karl Urban

deck: Canadian artist and writer. Worked briefly for Warren Publishing in the 1970s.
description:
Bruce Bezaire is an artist, minister and educator. He wrote several stories for Warren Publishing most famous of which was the four part serial "Night of the Jackass!" which appeared in Eerie magazine issues 60, 63-65 and was re-printed in it's entirety in Eerie issue 115.

He has also written and illustrated the three part comic series Dan Red Eagle for Indian Life Ministries.
name: Bruce Bezaire
